  <h1 class="h1">Family Business</h1>
  <p class="lede"><em>Family Business</em> is Charlotte’s current album project, exploring friendship, family dynamics, growing up, comparison, uncertainty, nostalgia, and the emotional stories people carry into adulthood.</p>

